# MernCrest Enterprise AI Platform — Part 01

Foundation for all work. Full bible: `PROJECT_DETAILS.md`.

## What this platform is

A complete **Enterprise Digital Business Platform** (company OS), not a brochure site.

MernCrest is primarily: Enterprise Technology · Software Development · AI Solutions · Cloud Consulting · Digital Transformation Partner.

Also sells (reseller only): Domains · Hosting · VPS · Cloud Hosting · SSL · Business Email.

## Non-negotiable business rules

- NEVER design as a hosting/infrastructure company
- NEVER assume MernCrest owns datacenters or hosting servers
- ALWAYS use Reseller Marketplace flow:

```text
Customer → MernCrest Platform → Provider API → Customer receives service
```

- Architecture MUST support multiple providers (configurable from Admin)
- Selling price = Provider price + configurable margin (Pricing Engine)

## Development rules

- NEVER remove existing features or break compatibility
- Improve architecture in place; do not rebuild from scratch
- TypeScript · Prisma · validated APIs · consistent JSON
- Separate UI from business logic; no duplicated domain logic
- New modules MUST integrate with: CRM, Notifications, Reports, Analytics, Permissions, Audit Logs

## Stack direction

Current: Next.js 14 App Router, React, Tailwind, shadcn/ui, PostgreSQL, Prisma, session RBAC.  
Target: Next.js 15, Session + JWT + RBAC, AWS (Docker, Nginx, PM2, Cloudflare), Redis.

## Design

Dark enterprise UI, purple brand, responsive, accessible, professional — match existing design system.

## Roles

Expand toward Guest / Customer / Sales / Support / Developer / Finance / HR / Manager / Administrator / Owner / CEO without breaking existing `CUSTOMER` | `STAFF` | `ADMIN` | `OWNER` guards.
